{"tid":358047,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★Apple 修改退貨政策 8月15日起 網上商店將不予退貨","createTime":"2017-08-13T12:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T04:24:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0cf93598cdf971776d2497b45b100b843f1d71d","tid":358047,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:33:23.000Z","msg":"每年 iPhone 新型號推出，都會有一番搶購潮，其中有不少人都是買來炒賣圖利。最近 Apple 就決定修改網上商店的條款，列明在網上商店購買的產品將不能退貨。<br />\n<br />\n現時 Apple 網上商店的退貨政策是，貨品售出後 14 日內可以退貨，但需要收取機價 15% 的退貨費用。不過在官方網頁上，最近就出現了一個新提示，表示退貨政策將於 2017 年 8 月 15 日起修改，而當日之後提交的訂單將適用新政策。如果在網上商店購買 iPhone，更直接標明新政策就是不接受退貨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/08/13/apple-aos-no-refund/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F08%2F13%2Fapple-aos-no-refund%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=sV9ypI8ORAQqPoRsufWwoP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=62208fef\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/08/13/apple-aos-no-refund/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"34277506871a4b287784f95c7ef69db357e70bb9","tid":358047,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:34:06.000Z","msg":"ifandog不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8a7e50855d290bf0f34c441e779bcc63670946","tid":358047,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:34:59.000Z","msg":"所有官方購買渠道，包括網上商店和Apple Store 實體（包括「iReserve」預約購買）都全部不接受退貨。Apple 從前的退貨條款相當寬鬆，不過近年就不斷收緊，而且只有香港地區才有特別政策禁止退貨。"},{"pid":"b44cc9c24272c5c29309cb8c92de11ba25df43a2","tid":358047,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:35:25.000Z","msg":"none buy Apple anymore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4c384d163973f2ded32e331c2a7f3177c07867","tid":358047,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只有香港地區才有特別政策禁止退貨。<br />\n只有香港地區才有特別政策禁止退貨。<br 